#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>You didn't import demo data?</strong> You can still do it. Go to "
"Apps &gt; Industries &gt; Upgrade your Hardware Shop package and check the "
"related box."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Nisi uvozil demo podatkov?</strong> Še vedno lahko to storite. "
"Pojdite v Aplikacijo &gt; Industrija &gt; Nadgradite svoj paket Hardware "
"Shop in označite ustrezno polje."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A free, personalized, integrated <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;"
"\">Website</span></strong> in a few clicks. Start receiving orders directly "
"in Odoo and go live with your <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">E-"
"shop</span></strong> in a few minutes."
msgstr ""
"Brezplačna, prilagojena in integrirana <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;"
"\">Spletna stran</span></strong> v nekaj klikih. Začnite prejemati naročila "
"neposredno v Odooju in zaženite svojo <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;"
"\">Spletno trgovino</span></strong> v nekaj minutah."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Ace Hardware is already registered in your database; select it using the "
"\"Customer\" button."
msgstr ""
"Ace Hardware je že registriran v vaši bazi podatkov; izberite ga z gumbom "
"»Stranka«."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "Add your customer, and the product they want."
msgstr "Dodajte svojo stranko in izdelek, ki ga želi."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Any specific manufacture process in your shop? (Cutting wood panels, "
"assemblies...). Try the <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Manufacture "
"App</span></strong>"
msgstr ""
"Imate v svoji delavnici kakšen specifičen proizvodni postopek? (Rezanje "
"lesenih plošč, sestavljanje ...). Preizkusite <strong><span style=\"color: "
"#875A7B;\">aplikacijo Izdelava</span></strong>"

