#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Hello there!\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            You just installed the Odoo for Hardware Shop package. By doing "
"so, we have installed a bunch of necessary apps to run your shop "
"efficiently.\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            Discover the basics of this package and explore all the "
"possibilities Odoo offers to improve your experience."
msgstr ""
"Pozdravljeni!\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            Pravkar ste namestili paket Odoo za trgovino s strojno opremo. S "
"tem smo namestili kup potrebnih aplikacij za učinkovito delovanje vaše "
"trgovine.\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            Odkrijte osnove tega paketa in raziščite vse možnosti, ki jih "
"Odoo ponuja za izboljšanje vaše izkušnje."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model:product.attribute.value,name:hardware_shop.product_attribute_value_7
msgid "High"
msgstr "Visok"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you go back to your Point of Sale, you can start a new order for 5 units "
"of Asian. Water Proofing Hydroloc for Ferrous Hardware, another B2B customer."
msgstr ""
"Če se vrnete na prodajno mesto, lahko začnete novo naročilo za 5 enot "
"azijskega hidroizolacijskega sistema Hydroloc za železno strojno opremo, še "
"eno stranko B2B."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you navigate to your \"Purchase App\", you can see that a new Purchase "
"Order for Ferrous Hardware has been automatically generated. It will ensure "
"a replenishment for Asian. Water Proofing Hydroloc."
msgstr ""
"Če odprete »Aplikacijo za nakup«, lahko vidite, da je bila samodejno "
"ustvarjena nova naročilnica za železno okovje. To bo zagotovilo dopolnitev "
"zalog za azijsko hidroizolacijo Hydroloc."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to execute a practical guided tour of this module, you should "
"Import demo data and try the Use Case."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvesti praktičen voden ogled tega modula, uvozite predstavitvene "
"podatke in preizkusite primer uporabe."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model:product.template,name:hardware_shop.product_template_104
msgid "JK Wall Putty Fine"
msgstr "JK zidni kit fini"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Let's say your customer Ace Hardware just called you to order 30 Asian. "
"Water Proofing Hydroloc."
msgstr ""
"Recimo, da vas je vaša stranka Ace Hardware pravkar poklicala, da bi "
"naročila 30 azijskih hidroizolacijskih izdelkov Hydroloc."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage all your communication channels in one place with Odoo <strong><span "
"style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Marketing Automation</span></strong>, "
"<strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Email Marketing</span></strong>, "
"<strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Social Media Marketing</span></"
"strong>, and <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">SMS Marketing</span></"
"strong>"
msgstr ""
"Upravljajte vse svoje komunikacijske kanale na enem mestu z "
"Odoo<strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Avtomatizacija trženja</span></"
"strong>, <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">E-poštno trženje</span></"
"strong>, <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Trženje na družbenih "
"omrežjih</span></strong>, in<strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">SMS "
"trženje</span></strong>"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your accounting easier than ever with a completely integrated "
"environment. (<strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Accounting App</span></"
"strong>)"
msgstr ""
"Upravljajte svoje računovodstvo lažje kot kdaj koli prej s popolnoma "
"integriranim okoljem. (<strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Računovodska "
"aplikacija</span></strong>)"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model:product.template,name:hardware_shop.product_template_70
msgid "Mario Super Water Tank"
msgstr "Mario Super rezervoar za vodo"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Navigate to the Inventory App and select \"X to process\" in the Delivery "
"Orders."
msgstr ""
"Pomaknite se do aplikacije Zaloga in v razdelku Naročila za dostavo izberite "
"»X za obdelavo«."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Navigate to your Sales App. You can now create a new Sales Order by clicking "
"the \"New\" button, top left."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite v svojo prodajno aplikacijo. Zdaj lahko ustvarite novo prodajno "
"naročilo s klikom na gumb »Novo« zgoraj levo."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Notice that if you need the delivery to be paid by your customer, you can "
"create a delivery product and add it to its cart. In this demo, you can use "
"the \"POS Delivery\" to add a 5,00 Excl. Taxes delivery price."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da če želite, da dostavo plača vaša stranka, lahko ustvarite "
"izdelek za dostavo in ga dodate v košarico. V tej predstavitvi lahko "
"uporabite »Dostava POS«, da dodate ceno dostave v višini 5,00 brez DDV."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Now that we have placed all these orders, it's time to purchase missing "
"products."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj, ko smo oddali vsa ta naročila, je čas za nakup manjkajočih izdelkov."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to turn your phone into "
"an additional scanner (and much more)."
msgstr ""
"Odoo je v celoti integriran v aplikacijo. Prenesite jo in svoj telefon "
"spremenite v dodaten skener (in še veliko več)."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as:"
msgstr "Odoo vam ponuja neskončne možnosti, kot so:"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"Seveda je to le pregled funkcij, ki so vključene v ta paket. Dodajate lahko "
"nove aplikacije, brišete/spreminjate demo podatke in preizkušate vse!"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once the order is placed, you can see that the top left button switches to "
"\"Receive products\". Click it to open your receipt order and validate it to "
"confirm that this product is back in stock."
msgstr ""
"Ko je naročilo oddano, lahko vidite, da se zgornji levi gumb preklopi na "
"»Prejem izdelkov«. Kliknite ga, da odprete potrdilo o naročilu in ga "
"potrdite, da potrdite, da je ta izdelek spet na zalogi."

