msgstr ""
"Z <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">aplikacijo Barcode</span></strong> "
"lahko skenirate svoje izdelke in ustvarite nove vnose neposredno iz te "
"aplikacije, da kodirate nove izdelke hitreje kot kdaj koli prej."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Inventory App</span></"
"strong> to manage your orders receive and deliver your products."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">aplikacijo Zaloga</span></"
"strong> za upravljanje naročil, prejemanje in dostavo izdelkov."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Point of Sale</span></"
"strong> for your sales at the desk. You can directly order new products for "
"your customers and manage their accounts and advantages. You will also have "
"the possibility to sale in your shop and choose to ship later the order."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Prodajno mesto</span></"
"strong> za prodajo na pultu. Nove izdelke lahko neposredno naročite za svoje "
"stranke in upravljate njihove račune ter ugodnosti. Imeli boste tudi možnost "
"prodaje v svoji trgovini in možnost poznejše odpreme naročila."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Purchase App</span></strong> "
"to order products from your suppliers."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">aplikacijo Nabava</span></"
"strong> za naročanje izdelkov pri dobaviteljih."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Sales App</span></strong> to "
"create quotations/sales orders for your business clients and invoice them on "
"the go using the <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Invoicing App</"
"span></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite<strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">aplikacijo Prodaja</span></"
"strong> za ustvarjanje ponudb/prodajnih naročil za svoje poslovne stranke in "
"jim izstavljajte račune na poti z aplikacijo za <strong><span style=\"color: "
"#875A7B;\">Izstavljanje računov</span></strong>."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "Validate the shipment with the top left main button."
msgstr "Pošiljko potrdite z zgornjim levim glavnim gumbom."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model:pos.category,name:hardware_shop.pos_category_delivery
msgid "Various"
msgstr "Različno"

