#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Welcome your customer Ace Hardware, a B2B customer. They need 2 Aqua Double "
"Soap Dish."
msgstr ""
"Pozdravite svojo stranko Strojna oprema Ace, stranko B2B. Potrebuje 2 dvojni "
"posodi za milo Aqua."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:web_tour.tour,rainbow_man_message:hardware_shop.knowledge_tour
msgid "Welcome! Happy exploring."
msgstr "Dobrodošli! Veselo raziskovanje."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model:product.attribute.value,name:hardware_shop.product_attribute_value_4
msgid "White"
msgstr "Bela"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr "Bi se radi z nami pogovorili o svoji nastavitvi Odoo ali šli še dlje?"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Do vsake nameščene aplikacije v vaši bazi podatkov Odoo lahko dostopate na "
"glavni nadzorni plošči."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can observe that the Purchase Order suggests a replenishment of 100 "
"products. This is due to the existing \"Reordering rule\" on this specific "
"product. \n"
"                    <br/><br/>\n"
"                    The reordering rule will ensure that our stock doesn't "
"go below the minimum quantity indicated and replenishes to the maximum "
"quantity encoded."
msgstr ""
"Opazili boste, da naročilnica predlaga dopolnitev 100 izdelkov. To je "
"posledica obstoječega \"pravila za ponovno naročanje\" za ta specifični "
"izdelek. \n"
"                    <br/><br/>\n"
"                    Pravilo za ponovno naročanje bo zagotovilo, da naša "
"zaloga ne bo padla pod navedeno minimalno količino in se bo dopolnila do "
"kodirane maksimalne količine."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can see that Ace Hardware benefits from a specific pricelist rebate of "
"5% on everything they buy. Manage pricelists by navigating to Products &gt; "
"Pricelists."
msgstr ""
"Vidite lahko, da ima Ace Hardware na vse, kar kupi, poseben cenik popust v "
"višini 5 %. Cenike lahko upravljate v razdelku Izdelki > Ceniki."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"Zaključili ste ta primer uporabe za demonstracijo! Obstaja na milijone "
"drugih načinov, kako prilagoditi svojo Odoo nastavitev svojim poslovnim "
"potrebam."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just need to send the Request For Quotation by email, or to confirm it "
"manually once the order is placed."
msgstr ""
"Zahtevo za ponudbo morate le poslati po e-pošti ali jo ročno potrditi, ko je "
"naročilo oddano."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of "
"various flows you can quickly implement with this package using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Za pregled različnih tokov, ki jih lahko hitro implementirate s tem paketom "
"z uporabo Odooja, bi morali biti sposobni izvesti naslednje poteke."

